```
apiVersion: v1 ![1](Images/1.png)
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
    name: configuration-data
data: ![2](Images/2.png)
    backgroundColor: blue
    title: Learning Helm
```

```
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
    name: example-pod
spec:
    volumes: ![1](Images/1.png)
    - name: my-configuration
      configMap:
        name: configuration-data ![2](Images/2.png)
    containers:
    - image: "nginx:latest"
      name: example-nginx
      env: ![3](Images/3.png)
        - name: BACKGROUND_COLOR ![4](Images/4.png)
          valueFrom:
            configMapKeyRef:
                name: configuration-data ![5](Images/5.png)
                key: backgroundColor ![6](Images/6.png)
```

```
apiVersion: apps/v1 ![1](Images/1.png)
kind: Deployment
metadata:
    name: example-deployment
    labels:
        app: my-deployment
spec:
    replicas: 3 ![2](Images/2.png)
    selector:
        matchLabels:
            app: my-deployment
    template: ![3](Images/3.png)
        metadata:
            labels:
                app: my-deployment
        spec:
            containers:
            - image: "nginx:latest"
              name: example-nginx
```

```
apiVersion: v1 ![1](Images/1.png)
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: example-service
spec:
  selector:
    app: my-deployment ![2](Images/2.png)
  ports:
    - protocol: TCP ![3](Images/3.png)
      port: 80
      targetPort: 8080
```
